statements: SELECT * FROM spare_parts_inventory;
SELECT part_id, part_name, quantity FROM spare_parts_inventory;
SELECT part_name, part_type FROM spare_parts_inventory WHERE quantity > 10;
SELECT * FROM spare_parts_inventory WHERE cost < 50.00;
SELECT part_type, quantity, cost, part_name FROM spare_parts_inventory ORDER BY quantity DESC;
SELECT * FROM spare_parts_inventory ORDER BY part_name DESC;
SELECT part_name, part_type, quantity FROM spare_parts_inventory WHERE cost > 50;
SELECT part_name, part_type FROM spare_parts_inventory WHERE quantity < 5 ORDER BY quantity DESC;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_parts, SUM(quantity) AS total_quantity FROM spare_parts_inventory;
SELECT part_id, cost FROM spare_parts_inventory WHERE part_type LIKE '%engine%' ORDER BY cost ASC;
SELECT * FROM spare_parts WHERE part_category = 'Engine';
SELECT part_name, unit_price FROM spare_parts ORDER BY unit_price DESC;
SELECT part_id, part_category, quantity FROM spare_parts WHERE quantity > 10;
SELECT part_name, part_category, unit_price FROM spare_parts WHERE unit_price BETWEEN 50 AND 100;
SELECT * FROM robot_components WHERE supplier_id IS NULL;
SELECT part_name, part_category FROM spare_parts WHERE quantity > 50 ORDER BY part_category DESC;
SELECT * FROM spare_parts WHERE unit_price < 100 ORDER BY part_id;
SELECT part_name, quantity, unit_price FROM spare_parts WHERE part_category = 'Electronics' AND quantity > 20 ORDER BY unit_price ASC;
SELECT part_name, part_category, unit_price FROM spare_parts WHERE part_category LIKE '%Bolts%' OR part_category LIKE '%Screws%' ORDER BY part_name;
SELECT component_name, component_type, quantity FROM robot_components WHERE supplier_id IS NOT NULL ORDER BY component_type ASC, quantity DESC;
SELECT * FROM spare_parts;
SELECT name, quantity FROM spare_parts WHERE quantity > 0;
SELECT name, price FROM spare_parts WHERE price < 100;
SELECT * FROM components WHERE available = true;
SELECT robots.name, components.name FROM robots JOIN components ON robots.component_id = components.component_id;
SELECT * FROM spare_parts WHERE quantity > 10 ORDER BY name DESC, price ASC;
SELECT name, quantity, price FROM spare_parts WHERE price > 100 ORDER BY quantity DESC;
SELECT s.name, c.name AS component_name, r.name AS robot_name FROM spare_parts s INNER JOIN components c ON s.spare_part_id = c.component_id INNER JOIN robots r ON c.component_id = r.component_id;

SELECT s.name AS spare_part_name, c.name AS component_name, r.name AS robot_name FROM robots r INNER JOIN components c ON r.component_id = c.component_id INNER JOIN spare_parts s ON c.component_id = s.spare_part_id;
SELECT * FROM components WHERE available = TRUE ORDER BY component_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM SpareParts;
SELECT part_name, quantity, unit_price FROM SpareParts WHERE quantity > 20;
SELECT * FROM Components ORDER BY unit_cost DESC;
SELECT component_name, category FROM Components WHERE in_stock = TRUE;
SELECT robot_id, manufacturing_date FROM Robots WHERE warranty_expiry_date < '2023-01-01';
SELECT * FROM SpareParts WHERE quantity > 0 ORDER BY part_name DESC;
SELECT part_name, unit_price FROM SpareParts WHERE unit_price > 100 ORDER BY unit_price ASC;
SELECT robot_name, manufacturing_date FROM Robots WHERE manufacturing_date BETWEEN '2022-05-01' AND '2022-05-31';
SELECT part_name, unit_price, supplier_id FROM SpareParts WHERE unit_price < 50 AND supplier_id = 3 ORDER BY part_name ASC;
SELECT robot_name, warranty_expiry_date FROM Robots WHERE warranty_expiry_date < '2023-01-01';
SELECT * FROM SpareParts LIMIT 5
SELECT part_name, quantity, price FROM SpareParts WHERE quantity > 10
SELECT part_name, part_description FROM SpareParts WHERE price < 100.00
SELECT component_name, component_type FROM Components ORDER BY component_type DESC
SELECT robot_name, manufacturing_date FROM Robots WHERE manufacturing_date > '2022-01-01'
SELECT * FROM SpareParts WHERE price > 100 ORDER BY part_name ASC;
SELECT robot_name, manufacturing_date FROM Robots WHERE component_id IN (SELECT component_id FROM Components WHERE component_type = 'Arm') ORDER BY manufacturing_date DESC;
SELECT robot_name, quantity FROM Robots JOIN RobotInventory ON Robots.robot_id = RobotInventory.robot_id WHERE location = 'Warehouse' ORDER BY quantity DESC, robot_name ASC;
SELECT part_name, part_description, price FROM SpareParts WHERE part_name LIKE '%gear%' AND quantity > 0 ORDER BY price DESC;

SELECT robot_name, maintenance_date, maintenance_description FROM Robots JOIN MaintenanceLogs ON Robots.robot_id = MaintenanceLogs.robot_id WHERE maintenance_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30' ORDER BY maintenance_date ASC;
